00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:01,500
They have collected

289
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:02,340
it.

290
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:05,100
I gave Chu Zhao my word.

291
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:07,300
As long as I draw breath,

292
00:18:09,140 --> 00:18:10,900
Yanlai shall not die.

293
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:16,780
I cannot break faith with her.

294
00:18:31,460 --> 00:18:32,100
Your Highness,

295
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:34,420
Mr. Xie

296
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:35,820
vomited blood again this morning.

297
00:18:36,540 --> 00:18:37,420
The Imperial Physician fears

298
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:40,340
he may not survive the winter.

299
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:44,180
How many days remain

300
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:46,740
until His Majesty's twelfth birthday?

301
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:48,140
Your Highness.

302
00:18:49,020 --> 00:18:50,660
Twenty-five days.

303
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:56,140
Twenty-five days.

304
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:08,420
It seems

305
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:12,780
I cannot pull through after all.

306
00:19:12,980 --> 00:19:14,100
Mr. Xie, please do not say

307
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:14,900
such ominous things.

308
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:19,180
Why fear death?

309
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:23,740
Yu is about to take the reins himself,

310
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:26,820
and he carries

311
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:30,740
the blood of the Xie Family.

312
00:19:30,820 --> 00:19:32,340
Yet should anything happen to you,

313
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:33,660
and Her Highness seizes this chance to consolidate power...

314
00:19:36,340 --> 00:19:38,260
I sacrificed so many lives

315
00:19:39,300 --> 00:19:40,740
to forge an emperor

316
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:42,180
from the Xie Family.

317
00:19:43,380 --> 00:19:45,460
I will not let that effort go to waste.

318
00:19:46,540 --> 00:19:47,220
No one can resist

319
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:49,340
the allure of power,

320
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,380
especially

321
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:54,940
a young emperor.

322
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:58,420
A true emperor

323
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:00,540
will never endure

324
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:02,140
being a puppet for a lifetime.

325
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:05,340
Once Yu assumes direct rule,

326
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:08,540
he will never tolerate

327
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:10,660
Chu Zhao's manipulation.

328
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:13,780
When the time comes,

329
00:20:14,700 --> 00:20:16,660
we shall give him one final push.

330
00:20:19,060 --> 00:20:21,140
I have an agreement with Yu.

331
00:20:23,100 --> 00:20:24,220
The very first decree

332
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,820
he issues upon assuming direct rule

333
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:31,020
shall be the annihilation of the Chu Clan.

334
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:38,260
Your Majesty,

335
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:40,780
the military treatise...

336
00:20:42,740 --> 00:20:44,260
I have no desire to learn such things today.

337
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:49,900
Uncle Yanfang said

338
00:20:50,900 --> 00:20:53,780
that reading people is like reading the stars.

339
00:20:57,220 --> 00:20:58,180
Your Majesty,

340
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:01,500
the art of reading the stars is for the imperial astronomers.

341
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:06,340
Grand Princess,

342
00:21:06,820 --> 00:21:07,780
I am the ruler,

343
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:09,700
and you are my subject.

344
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:14,340
Your Majesty will soon assume direct rule

345
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:16,260
and must weigh all matters carefully.

346
00:21:16,780 --> 00:21:17,860
This is for your good.

347
00:21:19,260 --> 00:21:20,300
For my good?

348
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:22,580
Search your heart.

349
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:25,300
Do you truly hope for me to rule,

350
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:26,540
or

351
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:28,860
are you desperate for me

352
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:29,900
to remain a puppet emperor

353
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:32,380
so you may keep the reins of power?

354
00:21:33,540 --> 00:21:34,140
Your Majesty,

355
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:35,500
I have never...

356
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,260
Never?

357
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:38,820
Why do you act with such high-handedness

358
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,900
whenever I face critical affairs of state?

359
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:43,220
Why do you obstruct me at every turn

360
00:21:43,580 --> 00:21:44,900
whenever I propose a different course?

361
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:46,740
Chu Zhao,

362
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,740
is the taste of absolute power

363
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:50,260
so sweet

364
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:51,700
that

365
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:55,140
you never intended to let go?

366
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:03,260
Is that truly how Your Majesty sees me?

367
00:22:03,460 --> 00:22:04,020
Enough.

368
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:06,700
Save your excuses.

369
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:08,100
Guards,

370
00:22:08,580 --> 00:22:10,580
escort the Grand Princess back to her palace

371
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:13,140
and confine her there to reflect on her transgressions.

372
00:22:21,460 --> 00:22:22,100
Your Majesty,

373
00:22:23,660 --> 00:22:25,780
please forgive my presumption.

374
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:39,540
Just as Young Master Yanfang expected.

375
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:08,900
Kneel.

376
00:23:10,460 --> 00:23:13,780
We congratulate Your Majesty on assuming direct rule.

377
00:23:17,420 --> 00:23:18,420
Ministers,

378
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:19,860
rise.

379
00:23:20,340 --> 00:23:21,820
- Thank you, Your Majesty. - Thank you, Your Majesty.

380
00:23:23,020 --> 00:23:23,860
My elder sister

381
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:26,700
entered Taiji Hall bearing the decree of supervising the court

382
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:28,980
and governed in my stead.

383
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:31,140
Now that the land is at peace

384
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:32,820
and I have assumed my rule,

385
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:35,100
she has earned her rest.

386
00:23:59,340 --> 00:24:00,500
I, Chu Zhao,

387
00:24:01,020 --> 00:24:02,980
congratulate Your Majesty on assuming direct rule.

388
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:26,420
I have an edict to announce.

389
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:29,700
Why would His Majesty deliver it

390
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:31,140
in person?

391
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:33,540
It is the first decree

392
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:34,780
of His Majesty's direct rule.

393
00:24:35,020 --> 00:24:36,380
It is of great significance.

394
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:40,540
Upon receiving this divine charge to govern the state,

395
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:41,940
I remain ever diligent,

396
00:24:42,100 --> 00:24:44,060
my thoughts centered solely on the state and its people.

397
00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:46,220
Chu Ling and Chu Zhao

398
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:56,900
have demonstrated steadfast loyalty,

399
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,740
ever mindful of the greater good of the state.

400
00:24:59,140 --> 00:25:00,980
The frontier is the shield of the state,

401
00:25:01,220 --> 00:25:02,300
upon which the state's security depends.

402
00:25:02,700 --> 00:25:04,780
Chu Ling, the Guard General,

403
00:25:05,340 --> 00:25:06,900
having stood guard at the frontier for decades,

404
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:09,660
repelled invaders and secured the state with extraordinary feats.

405
00:25:10,060 --> 00:25:11,260
Chu Zhao, the Grand Princess,

406
00:25:11,620 --> 00:25:14,100
left the palace to campaign in her father's stead.

407
00:25:14,260 --> 00:25:16,700
Peerless in valor, united in purpose with her father,

408
00:25:16,820 --> 00:25:18,620
she expanded and defended the state. Their monumental achievements stand

409
00:25:19,020 --> 00:25:21,300
as a glorious example for all subjects of the state to follow.

410
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:28,180
Yet Xie Yanfang, head of the Xie Clan,

411
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:29,900
steeped in generations of imperial favor

412
00:25:30,180 --> 00:25:31,300
and raised to one of the Three Excellencies,

413
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:33,460
was bound by duty to serve with utter devotion

414
00:25:33,740 --> 00:25:34,660
and uphold the order of the realm.

415
00:25:35,100 --> 00:25:37,140
Instead, harboring treacherous intent

416
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:38,500
and behaving with monstrous depravity,

417
00:25:38,820 --> 00:25:40,540
he colluded with the Northern Desert bandits

418
00:25:40,780 --> 00:25:41,820
to invite catastrophe,

419
00:25:42,260 --> 00:25:44,180
[Kill Zhong Changrong at Xinggu Pass]
leaving the frontier ravaged by war

420
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:45,980
and the populace displaced.

421
00:25:46,260 --> 00:25:48,620
By forming internal factions to purge the loyal,

422
00:25:48,820 --> 00:25:50,380
he sought to usurp power

423
00:25:50,580 --> 00:25:51,820
and deceive the throne,

424
00:25:52,100 --> 00:25:54,140
his crimes too numerous to recount.

425
00:25:54,620 --> 00:25:55,660
Most abhorrent

426
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:56,980
remains the tragedy at Wei Village,

427
00:25:57,460 --> 00:25:59,140
where for personal gain,

428
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:02,020
he emboldened foreign enemies to engage in arson and slaughter,

429
00:26:02,260 --> 00:26:03,700
sending the entire village

430
00:26:03,820 --> 00:26:04,900
to an unjust death.

431
00:26:05,100 --> 00:26:07,060
Such atrocities

432
00:26:07,180 --> 00:26:08,940
are beyond human reason,

433
00:26:09,180 --> 00:26:10,420
an abomination to all existence.

434
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:12,020
The laws of this land are unyielding,

435
00:26:12,300 --> 00:26:13,860
and they will not stand for such wicked defiance.

436
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:15,780
Though I ascended the throne in my youth,

437
00:26:16,100 --> 00:26:17,620
I bear the legacy of my ancestors

438
00:26:17,980 --> 00:26:19,420
and the trust of the people.

439
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:21,140
I shall act with uncompromising resolve

440
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:22,700
to purge all treachery and corruption.

441
00:26:23,100 --> 00:26:25,660
All titles and ranks of the Xie Clan are hereby stripped.

442
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:27,860
Their lands, estates, silver, and valuables

443
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:29,060
shall be confiscated.

444
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,660
All adult males of the Xie Clan

445
00:26:30,780 --> 00:26:32,140
shall be beheaded forthwith.

446
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:33,460
The women and children

447
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:34,780
shall be exiled to the far frontier as slaves.

448
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:37,220
Any pupils, former subordinates, or accomplices involved in his crimes

449
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,580
must surrender within ten days.

450
00:26:38,860 --> 00:26:41,220
Those captured after the deadline shall face punishment threefold.

451
00:26:41,500 --> 00:26:43,820
This decree is proclaimed across the state.

452
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:45,420
Whoever colludes with the enemy, betrays the state,

453
00:26:45,700 --> 00:26:47,060
or harms the people

454
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:48,180
shall be executed

455
00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:49,460
with their entire clan,

456
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:50,700
to uphold the laws of the state

457
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,980
and serve as a warning to all.

458
00:26:52,340 --> 00:26:53,900
May my ministers and I together

459
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:56,500
purge this corruption and restore a prosperous age.

460
00:26:57,460 --> 00:26:58,780
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

461
00:26:59,180 --> 00:27:01,500
Mr. Xie is your own in-law.

462
00:27:01,900 --> 00:27:02,900
Censor, mind your words.

463
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:04,100
I am a Xiao,

464
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:05,380
not a Xie.

465
00:27:06,100 --> 00:27:08,660
The state belongs to the Xiao Family.

466
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:10,500
I bring down the Xie Family

467
00:27:10,980 --> 00:27:12,420
to save all the people.

468
00:27:13,620 --> 00:27:14,380
Issue the decree.

469
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:16,060
Kowtow!

470
00:27:33,020 --> 00:27:33,540
Mr. Xie,

471
00:27:33,820 --> 00:27:34,380
His Majesty

472
00:27:34,900 --> 00:27:36,260
has decreed that your clan be purged.

473
00:27:48,220 --> 00:27:49,260
What did you say?

474
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:50,980
This is the imperial edict

475
00:27:51,260 --> 00:27:52,580
His Majesty announced during this morning's court session.

476
00:27:53,060 --> 00:27:54,620
He proclaimed that Chu Ling and Chu Zhao's monumental achievements

477
00:27:54,820 --> 00:27:55,660
shall be honored by the state,

478
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:56,820
while you are guilty

479
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:58,780
of heinous crimes,

480
00:27:59,140 --> 00:28:00,300
and your entire clan

481
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:01,980
is to be utterly eradicated.

482
00:28:23,020 --> 00:28:24,140
Absurd.

483
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:28,740
Profoundly absurd.

484
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:32,340
How dare he?

485
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:38,260
Mr. Xie, we must leave at once.

486
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:39,980
The Imperial Guard will reach Gaoyang shortly.

487
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:44,980
Leave?

488
00:28:47,740 --> 00:28:48,980
Where to?

489
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:51,780
Flee to the frontier

490
00:28:55,700 --> 00:28:57,580
or live in obscurity?

491
00:28:59,020 --> 00:29:00,860
How could I suffer

492
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:06,220
such humiliation?

493
00:29:06,660 --> 00:29:07,300
Mr. Xie,

494
00:29:08,140 --> 00:29:09,140
while there is life, there is hope.

495
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:10,300
We leave now

496
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:11,380
and figure out

497
00:29:11,540 --> 00:29:12,620
the rest later.

498
00:29:42,140 --> 00:29:46,420
[Xie Residence]
♪Xie Yanfang betrayed the state♪

499
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:51,420
♪And opened the door to the Northern Desert's blade♪

500
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:02,380
Zhao,

501
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:04,100
it is over.

502
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:10,300
Not yet.

503
00:30:50,020 --> 00:30:50,900
Your Highness,

504
00:30:52,580 --> 00:30:54,260
it took you long enough.

505
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:18,860
Look.

506
00:31:20,260 --> 00:31:21,740
Yanlai has finally gotten

507
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:24,140
exactly what he wanted.

508
00:31:28,420 --> 00:31:30,340
I remember him arriving at the Xie household

509
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:33,380
at eight years old.

510
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:35,740
He was so timid

511
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:38,300
and fearful of everything.

512
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:40,740
I held his hand

513
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:43,020
and taught him to read

514
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:44,820
[Xie Yanlai]
and write.

515
00:31:45,740 --> 00:31:47,380
The very first character he learned to write

516
00:31:49,460 --> 00:31:51,580
was Xie, as in our family name.

517
00:31:52,860 --> 00:31:54,020
I told him

518
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:57,180
never to forget

519
00:31:58,220 --> 00:31:59,740
his last name.

520
00:32:02,540 --> 00:32:03,580
Yet

521
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:06,700
the clan elders, disdaining his lowly origins,

522
00:32:07,940 --> 00:32:10,260
refused to grant him the surname.

523
00:32:11,380 --> 00:32:13,420
So, I sent him to the Wei village to handle that business,

524
00:32:14,540 --> 00:32:16,060
promising that if he succeeded,

525
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:18,660
I would persuade the elders

526
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:21,420
to add him to the genealogy.

527
00:32:23,660 --> 00:32:24,820
Back then...

528
00:32:26,060 --> 00:32:27,260
he was over the moon.

529
00:32:29,100 --> 00:32:30,260
He never knew

530
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:33,460
that I was the one who took Xiang...

531
00:32:35,780 --> 00:32:37,940
making him the lone scapegoat

532
00:32:38,540 --> 00:32:40,260
for the massacre at the Wei Village.

533
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:42,540
And while he was investigating

534
00:32:42,580 --> 00:32:44,220
the Xie Family's medicinal storage,

535
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:46,340
I had Du Qi

536
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:49,100
kill the boy.

537
00:32:51,740 --> 00:32:53,020
He was just a child.

538
00:32:54,420 --> 00:32:55,580
What did he ever do to deserve that?

539
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:57,180
His only mistake

540
00:32:58,300 --> 00:33:00,140
was that, after five years of captivity,

541
00:33:00,780 --> 00:33:03,220
he still wanted to testify for Yanlai.

542
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:23,140
The irony of it all...

543
00:33:25,300 --> 00:33:26,460
is that the life-saving pill

544
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:29,780
is useless without the second pill.

545
00:33:30,220 --> 00:33:31,820
My intention

546
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:34,420
was that if Yanlai truly took it...

547
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:37,540
I could save him

548
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:40,660
when the poison set in,

549
00:33:40,900 --> 00:33:42,060
and he would be indebted to me

550
00:33:42,060 --> 00:33:43,700
for life.

551
00:33:47,300 --> 00:33:48,620
It comes back to me now.

552
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:52,020
By a twist of fate,

553
00:33:52,900 --> 00:33:55,540
that is how your father met his end.

554
00:33:58,740 --> 00:34:01,180
Not entirely bad news, I suppose.

555
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:13,460
Chu Zhao,

556
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:17,020
you may bring down the Xie Family,

557
00:34:17,500 --> 00:34:19,980
but you cannot save Xie Yanlai.

558
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:23,140
The Golden Finch Venom has no cure.

559
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:25,660
He will die,

560
00:34:26,860 --> 00:34:30,660
and even before I do.

561
00:34:55,700 --> 00:34:56,860
Yanfang,

562
00:34:57,900 --> 00:34:59,220
despite all your calculating,

563
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:02,020
you are still one move behind.

564
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:23,860
Yanlai?

565
00:35:25,020 --> 00:35:26,260
Impossible.

566
00:35:29,260 --> 00:35:31,260
How are you still alive?

567
00:35:32,380 --> 00:35:33,420
Because all of this

568
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:37,580
was a trap laid carefully for you.

569
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:40,900
This dagger is forged with two sides,

570
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:43,780
distinguished by gold and silver.

571
00:35:45,100 --> 00:35:46,100
I will coat the gold side

572
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:48,700
with Golden Finch Venom in advance.

573
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:51,300
We are going to stage a death scene

574
00:35:51,340 --> 00:35:52,340
right before his eyes.

575
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:55,700
You will strike yourself with the silver, non-poisonous blade.

576
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:56,660
The wound, however,

577
00:35:57,900 --> 00:35:59,220
must look absolutely real.

578
00:36:00,500 --> 00:36:01,780
Only a lie built upon a grain of truth

579
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,260
can deceive them all.

580
00:36:04,180 --> 00:36:06,020
I will play the part of a hostage, forced back to the court

581
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:08,860
to serve as his puppet, day after day.

582
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:14,300
♪Numerous people are under my control♪

583
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:17,660
I could kill Xie Yanfang,

584
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:19,340
even at the cost of my own life.

585
00:36:19,780 --> 00:36:20,180
No.

586
00:36:20,780 --> 00:36:21,900
There will always be

587
00:36:22,340 --> 00:36:23,740
another Xie Yanfang.

588
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:25,940
We must leverage the Xie Family's influence

589
00:36:26,020 --> 00:36:26,980
to keep the court in check,

590
00:36:27,640 --> 00:36:28,900
until Yu takes the reins.

591
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:30,740
Yes, Your Highness.

592
00:36:33,940 --> 00:36:35,100
From that moment on,

593
00:36:35,660 --> 00:36:37,460
everything you saw was a lie.

594
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:40,580
I knew you were after the Frontier Troops Token,

595
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:42,660
so I instructed Zhong

596
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:43,860
to feign submission.

597
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:46,420
What I failed to account for

598
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:48,460
was how far you would sink,

599
00:36:48,460 --> 00:36:49,580
raising your blades against the Longwei Army.

600
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:51,700
This is the medicine Xie Yanfang sent.

601
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:53,500
Using the cover of my convalescence

602
00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:54,260
at Cangmu Stronghold,

603
00:36:54,780 --> 00:36:56,420
I've been quietly gathering evidence of the Xie Family's crimes.

604
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,020
Yet you were so intoxicated

605
00:36:58,020 --> 00:36:59,500
by the thrill of pulling every string

606
00:36:59,980 --> 00:37:00,900
that you let your guard down entirely.

607
00:37:00,980 --> 00:37:02,740
The officials you have promoted

608
00:37:03,220 --> 00:37:04,380
also allowed me to compile a complete list

609
00:37:04,380 --> 00:37:05,740
of the Xie Family's faction

610
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:06,660
within the court.

611
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:07,860
Jiu and I

612
00:37:08,780 --> 00:37:09,420
have always been working

613
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,780
behind your back,

614
00:37:11,260 --> 00:37:12,020
tirelessly molding Yu

615
00:37:12,020 --> 00:37:13,500
into a capable ruler.

616
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,180
Yunzhong Prefecture

617
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:17,060
is the frontier stronghold of the Capital,

618
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:18,220
easy to defend and hard to breach.

619
00:37:18,620 --> 00:37:20,020
But should the Northern Desert resolve its internal strife,

620
00:37:20,020 --> 00:37:20,860
return with force,

621
00:37:21,260 --> 00:37:22,940
and bring the surrounding minor states into the fold,

622
00:37:23,340 --> 00:37:25,540
a flanking assault could spell trouble.

623
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:27,020
May I then send envoys

624
00:37:27,180 --> 00:37:28,780
to build ties with neighboring states and avoid war?

625
00:37:29,020 --> 00:37:30,500
A wise thought, Your Majesty.

626
00:37:31,660 --> 00:37:32,780
Military strength and diplomacy

627
00:37:33,100 --> 00:37:34,020
are both essential

628
00:37:34,060 --> 00:37:35,420
to the art of governance.

629
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:38,300
Bear in mind that the greatest victory is to avoid war.

630
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,260
Peace

631
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:41,620
is what endures.

632
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:43,740
Hold the sword as you would a fist.

633
00:37:44,420 --> 00:37:46,580
Loosen your grip even once, and all is lost.

634
00:37:48,220 --> 00:37:49,700
Zhao, I understand.

635
00:37:51,580 --> 00:37:53,100
Ruling is like a game of strategy.

636
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:54,740
It matters not who moves first,

637
00:37:55,180 --> 00:37:57,980
only who has the last laugh.

638
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,740
♪Schemes within schemes, I prison myself♪

639
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:03,180
Much like what you are doing now.

640
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:08,640
♪The world is my Weiqi game board♪

641
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:11,700
♪Everything's just fleeting♪

642
00:38:11,700 --> 00:38:12,500
Yanfang,

643
00:38:12,980 --> 00:38:15,060
you always said the noble families were deeply entangled.

644
00:38:16,580 --> 00:38:18,260
So we learned from you,

645
00:38:18,780 --> 00:38:21,820
traced each root to its source,

646
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:23,340
and

647
00:38:23,980 --> 00:38:25,260
pulled them all out.

648
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:33,220
Yanlai,

649
00:38:34,540 --> 00:38:35,620
since you are alive,

650
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:37,820
why not come home?

651
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:40,500
After I pass away,

652
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:42,660
the immense power of the Xie Family

653
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:43,620
and the position of clan head

654
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,260
will all be yours.

655
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:48,980
Why make such a choice?

656
00:38:50,580 --> 00:38:52,780
What exactly are you trying to do?

657
00:38:54,260 --> 00:38:55,180
No one reads hearts well

658
00:38:55,220 --> 00:38:56,420
as you do.

659
00:38:58,180 --> 00:38:59,260
How can you not know

660
00:39:00,260 --> 00:39:01,500
that what I want

661
00:39:02,900 --> 00:39:03,660
is to take

662
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:06,300
the Xie Family's century-old legacy with me to the grave?

663
00:39:20,220 --> 00:39:21,100
The clan elders

664
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:22,580
must regret not killing me

665
00:39:23,820 --> 00:39:25,580
when they could,

666
00:39:26,460 --> 00:39:27,820
only for me, too low-born

667
00:39:27,820 --> 00:39:29,020
to enter the genealogy

668
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:33,100
to end the Xie's bloodline for good.

669
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,060
Yanlai.

670
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:39,340
Seeing you like this, so deranged,

671
00:39:40,860 --> 00:39:42,860
I almost see myself.

672
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:47,580
Indeed.

673
00:39:48,900 --> 00:39:51,140
I am the baby wolf you spent years shaping.

674
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:54,540
Remember,

675
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:56,660
my brother?

676
00:39:59,820 --> 00:40:00,940
We've won

677
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:04,260
this game after all.

678
00:40:05,380 --> 00:40:06,220
Good.

679
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:09,700
Splendid.

680
00:40:18,740 --> 00:40:19,580
Yanfang,

681
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:21,260
do you know

682
00:40:21,900 --> 00:40:22,780
why you lost this game?

683
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:26,980
For all your plotting,

684
00:40:26,980 --> 00:40:28,100
you forgot one thing.

685
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:31,380
The most brilliant schemes

686
00:40:32,620 --> 00:40:34,020
are the ones that ensnare their maker.

687
00:40:35,340 --> 00:40:36,700
Xie Yanfang, you were so confident

688
00:40:37,100 --> 00:40:37,900
that you never doubted

689
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:38,900
you were the one

690
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:39,740
moving the pieces.

691
00:40:39,980 --> 00:40:41,740
Little did you know

692
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:43,100
the very web you wove

693
00:40:43,820 --> 00:40:45,380
would be the one to close around you.

694
00:40:46,660 --> 00:40:47,540
Surprising, isn't it?

695
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:49,940
The piece

696
00:40:51,020 --> 00:40:52,900
you thought to command at will

697
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:54,780
has made you

698
00:40:55,780 --> 00:40:57,820
a discarded pawn of fate.

699
00:41:14,380 --> 00:41:14,980
Mr. Xie,

700
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:17,060
Her Highness is but a woman.

701
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:18,540
What does she have

702
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:19,980
that makes you treat her

703
00:41:19,980 --> 00:41:20,860
so differently?

704
00:41:22,260 --> 00:41:22,900
She is...

705
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:25,940
different.

706
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:28,500
Chu Zhao.

707
00:41:47,260 --> 00:41:48,820
A move made is a move set.

708
00:41:50,060 --> 00:41:50,820
I lost.

709
00:41:52,420 --> 00:41:53,260
And I own it.

710
00:42:26,820 --> 00:42:28,220
I see no difference

711
00:42:28,900 --> 00:42:30,420
between people.

712
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:32,740
But once a difference appears,

713
00:42:33,500 --> 00:42:35,100
the heart tilts.

714
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:37,460
And a tilted heart

715
00:42:38,540 --> 00:42:41,340
becomes a prison.

716
00:42:46,620 --> 00:42:47,700
From this day onward,

717
00:42:48,500 --> 00:42:51,260
taxes across all prefectures shall be reduced by thirty percent.

718
00:42:51,940 --> 00:42:53,740
- Your Majesty is wise. - Your Majesty is wise.

719
00:42:54,180 --> 00:42:54,700
Furthermore,

720
00:42:55,300 --> 00:42:56,900
the laws of the State of Chu shall be revised.

721
00:42:57,700 --> 00:42:59,540
Anyone found colluding with foreign powers

722
00:43:00,140 --> 00:43:01,060
shall be held collectively responsible,

723
00:43:01,660 --> 00:43:02,820
and their entire clan shall be exterminated.

724
00:43:50,660 --> 00:43:54,460
♪Day after day, across these ancient hills♪

725
00:43:54,460 --> 00:43:58,260
♪Again and again, the old city cold and still♪

726
00:43:58,260 --> 00:44:01,020
♪Through dust and battle, I look back♪

727
00:44:01,020 --> 00:44:04,260
♪And find you waiting at journey's end♪

728
00:44:05,820 --> 00:44:09,700
♪Night after night, the hours drift on♪

729
00:44:09,700 --> 00:44:13,420
♪Year after year, our reunions end too soon♪

730
00:44:13,420 --> 00:44:18,140
♪Love so deep, yet fate so thin, why must it be so hard?♪

731
00:44:20,260 --> 00:44:24,180
♪Through joy and sorrow, we have shared it all♪

732
00:44:24,180 --> 00:44:27,980
♪Bound by a knowing no words can name♪

733
00:44:27,980 --> 00:44:31,420
♪Two lonely souls, huddling together for warmth♪

734
00:44:32,460 --> 00:44:34,580
No luck with the hares, so you're after me now?

735
00:44:34,860 --> 00:44:36,380
You're just easier to catch.

736
00:44:37,020 --> 00:44:38,300
Every creature on these grasslands

737
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:39,460
is cunning.

738
00:44:39,460 --> 00:44:42,820
♪I sigh at the whims of merciless fate♪

739
00:44:42,820 --> 00:44:43,780
I just had

740
00:44:45,180 --> 00:44:46,260
a nightmare.

741
00:44:47,940 --> 00:44:49,980
So even you have fears, General Xie?

742
00:44:51,300 --> 00:44:52,860
In the dream, death tore us apart.

743
00:44:56,300 --> 00:44:57,660
Don't say that.

744
00:44:58,620 --> 00:45:00,220
We still have many years ahead of us.

745
00:45:01,780 --> 00:45:02,380
Agreed.

746
00:45:04,740 --> 00:45:05,740
Then we shall guard

747
00:45:05,740 --> 00:45:06,780
Yunzhong Prefecture side by side,

748
00:45:07,780 --> 00:45:08,660
day after day,

749
00:45:09,980 --> 00:45:10,940
year after year,

750
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:12,700
to the very end.

751
00:45:15,500 --> 00:45:16,380
I intend

752
00:45:17,460 --> 00:45:18,940
to expand the place

753
00:45:19,620 --> 00:45:20,380
where I used to live.

754
00:45:21,860 --> 00:45:23,500
Why the rush to renovate?

755
00:45:24,180 --> 00:45:25,020
There is every reason.

756
00:45:37,100 --> 00:45:38,380
I want to marry you.

757
00:45:38,820 --> 00:45:41,060
♪Light shatters into silhouettes♪

758
00:45:41,060 --> 00:45:41,940
Let's build a home together.

759
00:45:43,620 --> 00:45:44,260
What do you say?

760
00:45:44,380 --> 00:45:49,660
♪A lingering mark on my palm♪

761
00:45:50,420 --> 00:45:55,660
♪Hooves thunder through the ashes of war♪

762
00:45:55,660 --> 00:46:01,100
♪Riding the wild wind straight into the dawn♪

763
00:46:03,100 --> 00:46:05,540
♪A vivid life♪

764
00:46:05,820 --> 00:46:08,100
♪Bathed in tears♪

765
00:46:08,940 --> 00:46:11,940
♪Surging toward the dawn♪

766
00:46:12,780 --> 00:46:17,380
♪Let it burn until there's nothing left♪

767
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:20,380
♪We crown our pain like glory♪

768
00:46:21,160 --> 00:46:22,840
In the eleventh month of the thirteenth year

769
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:23,760
of Xingping,

770
00:46:24,400 --> 00:46:26,280
the Grand Princess withdrew into seclusion on account of illness.

771
00:46:27,080 --> 00:46:30,480
The Yunzhong frontier troops established the Princess's encampment.

772
00:46:30,580 --> 00:46:32,380
♪I'd spend the rest of my life with you♪

773
00:46:32,380 --> 00:46:35,260
♪Even if longing turns to ash♪

774
00:46:35,260 --> 00:46:37,380
♪I'd still feel no fear♪

775
00:46:42,380 --> 00:46:47,500
♪You are the hope I sowed in bleakest dark♪

776
00:46:47,500 --> 00:46:53,660
♪Where a sharp blade rises from the dust♪

777
00:46:55,220 --> 00:46:57,380
♪A vivid life♪

778
00:46:57,980 --> 00:47:00,100
♪Bathed in tears♪

779
00:47:00,820 --> 00:47:03,300
♪Surging toward the dawn♪

780
00:47:04,820 --> 00:47:09,420
♪Let it burn until there's nothing left♪

781
00:47:09,940 --> 00:47:12,500
♪We crown our pain like glory♪

782
00:47:12,780 --> 00:47:15,540
♪Give that long-held wish a chance♪

783
00:47:16,580 --> 00:47:21,140
♪Let's run straight into the ruins♪

784
00:47:21,500 --> 00:47:24,540
♪I'd spend the rest of my life with you♪

785
00:47:24,540 --> 00:47:27,500
♪Even if longing turns to ash♪

786
00:47:27,500 --> 00:47:29,300
♪Into a timeless monument♪

787
00:47:33,320 --> 00:47:37,920
♪Broken walls and withered branches, trapped in the mire♪

788
00:47:38,200 --> 00:47:40,680
♪Yet still striving to reach for the sky♪

789
00:47:40,720 --> 00:47:44,760
♪My pride is torn down and my body is sacrificed♪

790
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:49,120
♪The spark smolders in the crack♪

791
00:47:49,200 --> 00:47:51,160
♪And roars in the blaze♪

792
00:47:51,240 --> 00:47:54,480
♪Burning the cold night until daybreak♪

793
00:47:54,640 --> 00:47:56,880
♪Fate imprisons me♪

794
00:47:57,040 --> 00:48:01,840
♪But I won't beg the abyss for mercy♪

795
00:48:01,840 --> 00:48:06,040
♪Even if hope is faint, I remain proud♪

796
00:48:06,040 --> 00:48:10,320
♪A mayfly will cross the ocean, however long it takes♪

797
00:48:10,320 --> 00:48:15,760
♪However it ends up, I'll go my own way♪

798
00:48:15,760 --> 00:48:17,720
♪With no fear of the distance♪

799
00:48:17,720 --> 00:48:21,440
♪Born from decay, fireflies still burn♪

800
00:48:21,440 --> 00:48:25,880
♪With sword in hand, I'll pierce the dawn♪

801
00:48:25,880 --> 00:48:31,240
♪Let these scars all over me become♪

802
00:48:31,240 --> 00:48:34,840
♪My new pride♪

803
00:48:49,640 --> 00:48:52,520
♪Peril is everywhere in the palace♪

804
00:48:52,520 --> 00:48:55,040
♪Yet I smile to nobody but you♪

805
00:48:55,040 --> 00:48:57,400
♪Amidst the chaos♪

806
00:48:57,400 --> 00:49:01,680
♪I'll always be with you♪

807
00:49:03,120 --> 00:49:05,240
♪The spark smolders in the crack♪

808
00:49:05,320 --> 00:49:07,280
♪And roars in the blaze♪

809
00:49:07,360 --> 00:49:10,600
♪Burning the cold night until daybreak♪

810
00:49:10,760 --> 00:49:13,000
♪Fate imprisons me♪

811
00:49:13,160 --> 00:49:17,960
♪But I won't beg the abyss for mercy♪

812
00:49:17,960 --> 00:49:22,160
♪Even if hope is faint, I remain proud♪

813
00:49:22,160 --> 00:49:26,440
♪A mayfly will cross the ocean, however long it takes♪

814
00:49:26,440 --> 00:49:31,880
♪However it ends up, I'll go my own way♪

815
00:49:31,880 --> 00:49:33,840
♪With no fear of the distance♪

816
00:49:33,840 --> 00:49:37,560
♪Born from decay, fireflies still burn♪

817
00:49:37,560 --> 00:49:42,000
♪With sword in hand, I'll pierce the dawn♪

818
00:49:42,000 --> 00:49:47,360
♪Let these scars all over me become♪

819
00:49:47,360 --> 00:49:50,960
♪My new pride♪
